summary: do you know how i can actually watch moominvalley from the moomin hunt doc tho? everytime ive tried to watch/download something...
question: do you know how i can actually watch moominvalley from the moomin hunt doc tho? everytime ive tried to watch/download something it says the video has been played/downloaded too much. i just need ep 2, 10 and 12, ive watched the other eps on kisscartoon but i cant seem to find these eps anywhere else :\
answer:
Yes I do, if you are on the computer, just left click over the episode and then create a copy, then just watch the copy. If you are on the phone, click onto the episode and it’ll say you can’t watch it. Click one of the three dots at the top and it should say open in another window, click that. You should be able to click the same three dots again and click “make a copy” and be able to watch it just fine

Edit: if you need the link to it again here:

MOOMIN HUNT - Google Drive

summary: hi I saw your post in the moomin tag idk if you'd have any idea bu is there a way to watch moominvalley in the US? sorry to...
question: hi I saw your post in the moomin tag idk if you'd have any idea bu is there a way to watch moominvalley in the US? sorry to bother you
answer: You’re not a bother at all, dear! Of course there is just search Moomin 1 on youtube and it’ll pull up the first episode. They won’t autoplay in order so you’ll have keep searching Moomin 2, Moomin 3 etc and its very important to watch them in order. There’s a continuous story line :)

summary: (Credit for banner goes to the ridiculously perfect @caiatra)  Okay, let’s try this again!! This is a promo post for my moomin...
body:
(Credit for banner goes to the ridiculously perfect @caiatra)

Okay, let’s try this again!!

This is a promo post for my moomin discord server, specifically tailored to LGBT folk who have fallen in love w/ the moomins, whether that love is old or new >:3c We’re a growing server & our mods do a lot of work to make sure that it is a comfortable and nice environment for LGBT fans of moomin to hang out!! 

A while ago I accidentally deleted my old blog, which unfortunately means that I don’t get notifs from my old server post anymore & it’s much harder to keep up with, so this is the new and updated version of the post - please like and/or reblog this post if you’d like a link! 

- This is an LGBT server, please don’t join if you’re cishet! 
- Minor safe but not exclusive to minors, however we tend to not let in folks over 21 yrs old
- dni if you’re into h//etalia or generally gross stuff lol

We’re excited to see you there!! >:3c

summary: Imagine an episode where, Moomin gets tricked into getting married Moomin asks Snufkin what a real relationship is Moomin and...
body:
Imagine an episode where,

  • Moomin gets tricked into getting married
  • Moomin asks Snufkin what a real relationship is
  • Moomin and Snukin go on a hike, just the two
  • Snufkin teaches Moomin how to survive in the wild
  • Snufkin watches Moomin sleep
  • Snufkin decides to lead Moomin home, where he belongs

And it could also tell us that the reason Moomin can’t come with Snufkin. It isn’t just because Snufkin likes to be alone, but also because he want’s Moomin to be safe and pure.
